    ns1:contribute-01.giver <http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/fred/domain.owl#research_1> .

<http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/fred/domain.owl#die_1> a <https://w3id.org/framester/data/propbank-3.4.0/RoleSet/die-01> ;
